usic/transgressive-records-to-celebrate-20th-anniversary-with-shows-from-mystery-jets-arlo-parks-marika-hackman-and-more-3761072">为庆祝成立 20 周年，Transgressive Records 推出了来自 Mystery Jets、Arlo Parks、Marika Hackman 等乐队的演出，并</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次亮相。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Arlo-Parks-Marika-Hackman-and-Mystery-Jets.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-Harry-Herd-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="阿洛·帕克斯、玛丽卡·哈克曼和神秘喷气机。图片来源：Joseph Okpako、Harry Herd 和 Lorne Thomson，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Arlo-Parks-Marika-Hackman-and-Mystery-Jets.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-Harry-Herd-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Arlo-Parks-Marika-Hackman-and-Mystery-Jets.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-Harry-Herd-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Arlo-Parks-Marika-Hackman-and-Mystery-Jets.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-Harry-Herd-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Arlo-Parks-Marika-Hackman-and-Mystery-Jets.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-Harry-Herd-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Arlo-Parks-Marika-Hackman-and-Mystery-Jets.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-Harry-Herd-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Arlo-Parks-Marika-Hackman-and-Mystery-Jets.-Credit-Joseph-Okpako-Harry-Herd-and-Lorne-Thomson-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Transgressive Records 宣布推出一系列特别活动，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mystery-jets">Mystery Jets</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Arlo-Parks">Arlo Parks</a>等，以庆祝其成立 20 周年。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/transgressive-fifteen-year-anniversary-foals-the-shins-celebration-2555570">只有马驹和狂欢：回顾 15 年的越轨记录</a></strong></li></ul><p>为了庆祝他们的里程碑，这个由唱片公司、发行商和管理公司组成的独立音乐团体与 War Child 和 Music Venue Trust 合作，宣布在伦敦举办一系列演出。</p><p>现场表演将包括 Mystery Jets、Arlo Parks、 <a href="/artists/Marika-Hackman">Marika Hackman</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Johnny-Flynn">Johnny Flynn</a> 、 <a href="/artists/The-Joy">The Joy</a>和 KOKOKO 等乐队！和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/2026987-2026987">登月</a>。这些演出将于今年晚些时候举行，并将在城市各地的标志性场所举行。</p><p>一般门票销售将于周五（5 月 31 日）开始。<a href="https://formpresents.com/shows/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处购买门票</a>并查看下面的完整演出列表。更多特别活动将在稍后公布。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C7g-TJftlTq/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.8